1
00:00:06,868 --> 00:00:07,427
Mr. Tu.

2
00:00:08,028 --> 00:00:08,668
- What's wrong?
- Manni.

3
00:00:09,188 --> 00:00:10,108
Go find Su Yunian.

4
00:00:10,108 --> 00:00:11,188
She's taken away.

5
00:00:12,108 --> 00:00:12,587
Also,

6
00:00:13,547 --> 00:00:14,508
I saw Qin Wei.

7
00:00:14,508 --> 00:00:15,264
Search together.

8
00:00:41,268 --> 00:00:42,228
Ms. Bai,

9
00:00:42,988 --> 00:00:44,308
long time no see.

10
00:00:46,628 --> 00:00:47,427
Wei,

11
00:00:48,507 --> 00:00:49,548
Mr. Tu said

12
00:00:50,187 --> 00:00:51,707
you're banned from here.

13
00:00:52,348 --> 00:00:53,268
Yes,

14
00:00:54,868 --> 00:00:55,868
he did say that.

15
00:00:56,507 --> 00:00:57,908
How heartless he is!

16
00:00:59,228 --> 00:01:00,387
He saw you just now.

17
00:01:00,868 --> 00:01:01,787
Didn't you know?

18
00:01:02,668 --> 00:01:03,467
I know.

19
00:01:04,067 --> 00:01:05,868
Look how nervous he gets.

20
00:01:06,868 --> 00:01:08,548
He fears I'll come

21
00:01:08,908 --> 00:01:10,627
for his new flame Su Yunian,

22
00:01:10,987 --> 00:01:12,508
just as I dealt with An Ruoxi

23
00:01:12,708 --> 00:01:13,987
in the old days.

24
00:01:14,267 --> 00:01:14,827
Manni,

25
00:01:15,668 --> 00:01:16,788
am I wrong?

26
00:01:17,588 --> 00:01:18,228
Wei,

27
00:01:18,508 --> 00:01:20,387
look what you've done
to yourself for him.

28
00:01:21,148 --> 00:01:21,907
Was it worth it?

29
00:01:22,508 --> 00:01:23,187
Yes.

30
00:01:23,708 --> 00:01:24,948
Absolutely worth it.

31
00:01:26,627 --> 00:01:28,228
If you're just following orders,

32
00:01:28,987 --> 00:01:30,987
you can order security right now

33
00:01:31,187 --> 00:01:32,267
to arrest me.

34
00:01:33,107 --> 00:01:34,267
I won't blame you.

35
00:01:36,987 --> 00:01:37,788
Remember this:

36
00:01:38,827 --> 00:01:39,987
don't touch Su Yunian.

37
00:01:51,872 --> 00:01:53,184
(Remotely access the security system?)

38
00:01:58,907 --> 00:01:59,588
Here.

39
00:02:02,588 --> 00:02:04,347
Elevator two of underground parking lot.

40
00:02:05,508 --> 00:02:06,752
Switch to the parking lot feed.

41
00:02:08,308 --> 00:02:09,267
Zoom in on this camera.

42
00:02:09,568 --> 00:02:10,688
(Temporarily disable camera?)

43
00:02:10,868 --> 00:02:11,907
Jiasheng,

44
00:02:12,948 --> 00:02:13,948
tonight,

45
00:02:14,708 --> 00:02:16,747
I'll give you

46
00:02:17,308 --> 00:02:23,388
a taste of old dreams rekindled.

47
00:02:27,548 --> 00:02:28,308
Mr. Tu, Ms. Bai.

48
00:02:28,308 --> 00:02:29,627
We really didn't do this.

49
00:02:31,328 --> 00:02:34,432
=The Glory Fades=

50
00:02:34,432 --> 00:02:37,184
=Episode 16=
(The Nightmare Repeats)

51
00:02:37,988 --> 00:02:38,988
Jiasheng,

52
00:02:39,747 --> 00:02:41,308
the Beauty Contest night

53
00:02:41,627 --> 00:02:45,507
is a little gift from me.

54
00:03:16,128 --> 00:03:18,848
(Signal lost)

55
00:03:27,747 --> 00:03:28,467
Manni,

56
00:03:29,308 --> 00:03:30,108
tell Lu

57
00:03:30,108 --> 00:03:30,947
to tighten security.

58
00:03:31,028 --> 00:03:31,627
Got it.

59
00:03:38,548 --> 00:03:39,988
I'm with Mr. Tu in the camera room.

60
00:03:41,187 --> 00:03:42,148
Okay, see you soon.

61
00:03:43,067 --> 00:03:43,747
Okay.

62
00:03:45,388 --> 00:03:46,108
Hello, Lu.

63
00:03:46,988 --> 00:03:48,588
Has Feng contacted you lately?

64
00:03:48,868 --> 00:03:49,667
Not at all.

65
00:03:56,868 --> 00:03:57,747
Can you fix it?

66
00:03:58,467 --> 00:04:00,108
Heipi from maintenance already left.

67
00:04:00,787 --> 00:04:02,028
The new bartender Chu Bai

68
00:04:02,028 --> 00:04:03,268
majored in this field.

69
00:04:03,747 --> 00:04:05,708
Get it fixed within 30 minutes.

70
00:04:05,947 --> 00:04:07,507
I'm heading to the parking lot now.

71
00:04:07,507 --> 00:04:13,708
(Signal lost)

72
00:04:13,708 --> 00:04:14,347
Chu Bai,

73
00:04:14,907 --> 00:04:16,067
come to camera room now.

74
00:04:23,028 --> 00:04:23,787
Ms. Su,

75
00:04:24,028 --> 00:04:24,907
no need to be nervous.

76
00:04:25,547 --> 00:04:26,907
It's not me who wants to see you.

77
00:04:27,307 --> 00:04:28,107
Not you?

78
00:04:28,388 --> 00:04:28,828
Yes.

79
00:04:28,867 --> 00:04:30,107
This is He Mike,

80
00:04:30,107 --> 00:04:30,708
our mayor.

81
00:04:36,388 --> 00:04:37,508
Hello, Miss Su.

82
00:04:37,948 --> 00:04:38,628
Please.

83
00:04:39,188 --> 00:04:39,748
Ms. Su,

84
00:04:39,948 --> 00:04:40,427
please.

85
00:05:42,467 --> 00:05:44,628
Oh Tu Jiasheng,

86
00:05:45,667 --> 00:05:48,107
turns out you can get nervous too.

87
00:05:53,508 --> 00:05:56,628
But you only panic over women, right?

88
00:05:56,948 --> 00:05:58,307
What you've mentioned

89
00:05:58,307 --> 00:06:00,588
would make juicy gossip for the news.

90
00:06:00,907 --> 00:06:01,787
However,

91
00:06:01,787 --> 00:06:03,107
An Ruoxi and I

92
00:06:03,307 --> 00:06:04,787
had no real connection.

93
00:06:06,068 --> 00:06:07,068
Also, Mr. He,

94
00:06:07,708 --> 00:06:08,708
I'm deeply sorry.

95
00:06:09,184 --> 00:06:11,008
I truly know nothing about

96
00:06:11,008 --> 00:06:12,307
what happened to He Cong.

97
00:06:12,708 --> 00:06:14,028
I've already told you

98
00:06:14,028 --> 00:06:15,508
everything happened that night.

99
00:06:17,347 --> 00:06:19,467
I knew my son's character well.

100
00:06:20,028 --> 00:06:22,547
I always disciplined him as needed.

101
00:06:22,828 --> 00:06:24,347
But I never imagined

102
00:06:24,828 --> 00:06:26,508
he'd lose his life,

103
00:06:28,547 --> 00:06:29,547
forcing me to endure

104
00:06:29,547 --> 00:06:32,148
the agony of outliving my child.

105
00:06:33,792 --> 00:06:34,880
I hope you

106
00:06:35,168 --> 00:06:37,268
understand my grief.

107
00:06:40,708 --> 00:06:42,068
Though it's a bit late,

108
00:06:42,708 --> 00:06:44,268
I still want to say it,

109
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,787
please accept my condolences.

110
00:06:47,227 --> 00:06:48,268
Miss Su,

111
00:06:49,028 --> 00:06:50,508
you act with integrity,

112
00:06:50,508 --> 00:06:51,708
and conduct yourself.

113
00:06:52,068 --> 00:06:52,948
However,

114
00:06:53,628 --> 00:06:56,268
Deep In The Bustle is a giant dye vat.

115
00:06:56,508 --> 00:06:58,547
Now that you've won the crown today,

116
00:06:59,188 --> 00:07:00,948
I hope you

117
00:07:00,948 --> 00:07:02,148
will think carefully

118
00:07:02,347 --> 00:07:03,388
and act prudently.

119
00:07:06,708 --> 00:07:08,068
Thank you for the reminder.

120
00:07:08,268 --> 00:07:09,268
I'll be cautious.

121
00:07:13,188 --> 00:07:14,068
In the future,

122
00:07:14,347 --> 00:07:16,667
if there's anything I can assist with,

123
00:07:16,867 --> 00:07:18,227
feel free to contact me.

124
00:07:20,256 --> 00:07:22,080
(He Mike, Mayor of Luolianke City)

125
00:07:36,547 --> 00:07:37,307
Mr. Tu.

126
00:07:37,307 --> 00:07:38,148
We haven't found her.

127
00:07:39,667 --> 00:07:40,347
Mr. Tu.

128
00:07:40,347 --> 00:07:41,588
We haven't found her either.

129
00:07:51,787 --> 00:07:53,508
Looking for me, Mr. Tu?

130
00:07:58,496 --> 00:07:59,427
Where did you go?

131
00:07:59,867 --> 00:08:00,828
Nowhere special.

132
00:08:01,028 --> 00:08:02,987
Just chatted with a guest for a while.

133
00:08:03,467 --> 00:08:05,347
Don't you know the rules
of Deep In The Bustle?

134
00:08:05,508 --> 00:08:06,547
Without permission,

135
00:08:06,547 --> 00:08:08,268
don't go out privately with guests.

136
00:08:08,467 --> 00:08:09,667
But I didn't go outside.

137
00:08:10,028 --> 00:08:11,867
I was just in the parking lot here.

138
00:08:15,907 --> 00:08:16,828
Mr. Tu,

139
00:08:17,948 --> 00:08:19,307
are you scared?

140
00:08:20,508 --> 00:08:21,907
I was worried about you.

141
00:08:22,148 --> 00:08:23,107
Worried about me?

142
00:08:24,107 --> 00:08:26,748
Worried I'd run
into another punk like Lin Shen?

143
00:08:27,148 --> 00:08:29,867
Or worried your enemies might target me?

144
00:08:33,508 --> 00:08:34,347
What enemies?

145
00:08:34,987 --> 00:08:35,787
For example,

146
00:08:36,227 --> 00:08:38,048
the real killer of An Ruoxi.

147
00:08:42,388 --> 00:08:43,348
Since you're fine,

148
00:08:43,587 --> 00:08:44,468
let's go upstairs.

149
00:08:58,268 --> 00:08:59,268
Thanks.

150
00:09:07,508 --> 00:09:08,228
How's it going?

151
00:09:08,228 --> 00:09:08,988
How much longer?

152
00:09:09,348 --> 00:09:10,348
Almost done, Ms. Bai.

153
00:09:16,028 --> 00:09:17,067
Where did you go?

154
00:09:17,307 --> 00:09:18,508
I'm fine, Ms. Bai.

155
00:09:18,748 --> 00:09:19,907
A guest just now

156
00:09:19,907 --> 00:09:20,832
asked to chat

157
00:09:20,832 --> 00:09:21,984
and have a drink in his car.

158
00:09:22,427 --> 00:09:23,228
So I

159
00:09:23,508 --> 00:09:24,667
didn't feel right refusing.

160
00:09:27,067 --> 00:09:28,868
You might not have wanted to refuse,

161
00:09:28,988 --> 00:09:30,988
but you could have told
any staff member,

162
00:09:31,228 --> 00:09:32,748
so we could have taken action

163
00:09:32,748 --> 00:09:33,827
to prevent any accidents.

164
00:09:34,988 --> 00:09:35,707
Well,

165
00:09:36,388 --> 00:09:38,187
even though I entered the contest,

166
00:09:38,508 --> 00:09:39,388
I'm still

167
00:09:39,988 --> 00:09:41,508
just a waitress, right?

168
00:09:47,547 --> 00:09:48,827
You'll be transferred tomorrow.

169
00:09:49,148 --> 00:09:49,787
How about that?

170
00:09:50,307 --> 00:09:50,907
Mr. Tu?

171
00:09:54,108 --> 00:09:54,947
Can it be fixed?

172
00:09:55,988 --> 00:09:57,028
Should be, Mr. Tu.

173
00:09:57,268 --> 00:09:58,587
The system was hacked.

174
00:09:58,787 --> 00:10:00,187
A whole set of code was destroyed.

175
00:10:00,787 --> 00:10:02,348
I'm deleting the corrupted parts now

176
00:10:02,348 --> 00:10:03,667
and rewriting a new set.

177
00:10:04,787 --> 00:10:05,468
I'll try.

178
00:10:05,468 --> 00:10:06,268
It should work.

179
00:10:08,067 --> 00:10:09,067
So complex.

180
00:10:10,067 --> 00:10:11,148
So they're a professional.

181
00:10:11,707 --> 00:10:12,628
Yes, indeed.

182
00:10:13,427 --> 00:10:14,787
And look at the history.

183
00:10:15,187 --> 00:10:16,667
It was hacked once before

184
00:10:16,667 --> 00:10:17,988
and was repaired then.

185
00:10:19,268 --> 00:10:20,307
The thing is,

186
00:10:20,508 --> 00:10:22,628
it's the same method in both incidents.

187
00:10:22,628 --> 00:10:23,508
Same?

188
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,936
(Three years ago)

189
00:10:28,547 --> 00:10:31,108
(Jiasheng, don't push your luck.)

190
00:10:31,187 --> 00:10:32,787
(And don't be so arrogant.)

191
00:10:33,187 --> 00:10:34,907
(Forget about that woman.)

192
00:10:35,427 --> 00:10:39,148
(Even Deep In The Bustle,
which you think is impregnable,)

193
00:10:39,508 --> 00:10:42,827
(can be destroyed by me anytime.)

194
00:10:46,468 --> 00:10:48,028
Mr. Tu, what brings you here?

195
00:10:58,208 --> 00:10:58,592
(Signal lost)

196
00:11:08,827 --> 00:11:09,307
Hello.

197
00:11:09,587 --> 00:11:10,427
What do you say?

198
00:11:11,187 --> 00:11:12,707
Today's little show is called

199
00:11:12,707 --> 00:11:14,187
The Gradual Disappearance.

200
00:11:14,667 --> 00:11:16,427
Those beautiful illusions

201
00:11:16,748 --> 00:11:18,988
will collapse one by one
before your eyes.

202
00:11:19,468 --> 00:11:21,228
I'm warning you for the last time.

203
00:11:21,228 --> 00:11:22,208
Follow orders

204
00:11:22,208 --> 00:11:23,628
and obey the plan.

205
00:11:24,108 --> 00:11:26,348
I'll give you the person you want most.

206
00:11:26,547 --> 00:11:27,508
But remember,

207
00:11:27,827 --> 00:11:29,108
(Signal lost)
don't be so greedy.

208
00:11:29,427 --> 00:11:30,187
One more thing.

209
00:11:30,547 --> 00:11:33,827
I can steady you
with just my fingertips.

210
00:11:33,947 --> 00:11:36,067
But the thunder in my palm

211
00:11:36,628 --> 00:11:39,468
always hangs over your head.

212
00:11:47,868 --> 00:11:49,868
Why didn't you finish the job cleanly?

213
00:11:50,348 --> 00:11:52,228
Why did you let her come back?

214
00:11:52,427 --> 00:11:53,748
This was Feng's plan.

215
00:11:53,748 --> 00:11:55,427
Why do you have so many questions?

216
00:11:55,628 --> 00:11:56,547
Where's Feng?

217
00:11:56,988 --> 00:11:57,988
Returned from abroad?

218
00:11:58,628 --> 00:11:59,348
I need to see him.

219
00:11:59,707 --> 00:12:01,028
You would've already seen him

220
00:12:01,148 --> 00:12:02,388
if he wanted to see you.

221
00:12:02,787 --> 00:12:05,268
You were by his side from the beginning.

222
00:12:05,508 --> 00:12:06,067
What?

223
00:12:06,268 --> 00:12:08,907
Can't even get to see him now?

224
00:12:08,947 --> 00:12:11,028
Stop bringing up our past.

225
00:12:11,388 --> 00:12:13,348
Feng hacked into the cameras.

226
00:12:13,547 --> 00:12:14,187
And I

227
00:12:14,348 --> 00:12:16,388
lured the tiger away from the mountain.

228
00:12:16,388 --> 00:12:17,707
What about you?

229
00:12:18,028 --> 00:12:18,827
Have your people

230
00:12:18,827 --> 00:12:20,468
got in Room 999?

231
00:12:20,748 --> 00:12:21,827
Have they found it?

232
00:12:21,868 --> 00:12:22,667
Get lost!

233
00:12:36,187 --> 00:12:36,988
Ms. Bai,

234
00:12:37,508 --> 00:12:38,988
no need to arrange a car for me.

235
00:12:39,427 --> 00:12:40,468
You're so busy.

236
00:12:41,547 --> 00:12:42,707
It's Mr. Tu's order,

237
00:12:43,468 --> 00:12:44,268
you know.

238
00:12:46,787 --> 00:12:48,907
Seems even before anything's happened,

239
00:12:49,707 --> 00:12:51,228
I've become everyone's target.

240
00:12:53,628 --> 00:12:54,587
Back in the day,

241
00:12:55,547 --> 00:12:58,268
was An Ruoxi treated
with this much importance too?

242
00:13:02,707 --> 00:13:03,508
Ms. Bai,

243
00:13:05,108 --> 00:13:06,187
you like Mr. Tu,

244
00:13:07,187 --> 00:13:07,868
right?

245
00:13:10,707 --> 00:13:11,587
At least,

246
00:13:12,028 --> 00:13:13,307
you used to like him a lot.

247
00:13:15,148 --> 00:13:16,787
It's all meaningless past.

248
00:13:19,748 --> 00:13:20,748
Ms. Bai,

249
00:13:21,707 --> 00:13:24,067
every path in life is meaningful.

250
00:13:24,868 --> 00:13:26,067
Even if the journey is hard,

251
00:13:26,707 --> 00:13:28,028
even if the ending is painful,

252
00:13:28,947 --> 00:13:30,667
one day you'll look back and realize

253
00:13:31,427 --> 00:13:32,268
this path

254
00:13:32,868 --> 00:13:34,348
was never walked in vain.

255
00:13:34,988 --> 00:13:35,787
So,

256
00:13:36,587 --> 00:13:37,667
have you found

257
00:13:37,947 --> 00:13:40,268
the meaning
of entering Deep In The Bustle?

258
00:14:02,427 --> 00:14:03,228
Rang but no answer.

259
00:14:03,868 --> 00:14:04,468
Call again.

260
00:14:18,108 --> 00:14:19,880
Try Merens
of Customs General Administration.

261
00:14:20,307 --> 00:14:21,187
Tell him to check

262
00:14:21,628 --> 00:14:22,988
any entry records of Feng.

263
00:14:24,547 --> 00:14:25,748
Okay, I'll arrange it.

264
00:14:26,108 --> 00:14:27,028
Get some rest now.

265
00:14:57,628 --> 00:14:58,427
Feng,

266
00:15:00,988 --> 00:15:03,028
what will it take for you to let me go?

267
00:15:09,587 --> 00:15:11,787
The weather is cloudy,
turning to sunny, then to rainy.

268
00:15:13,108 --> 00:15:15,827
Today's weather is a bit like my mood.

269
00:15:16,427 --> 00:15:17,148
I know

270
00:15:17,787 --> 00:15:19,907
that kind of place is a quagmire.

271
00:15:20,388 --> 00:15:21,108
(So)

272
00:15:22,388 --> 00:15:23,988
(when I walked through that door,)

273
00:15:25,067 --> 00:15:27,187
(my mood sank to its lowest point.)

274
00:15:28,108 --> 00:15:29,187
(But unexpectedly,)

275
00:15:30,348 --> 00:15:32,307
(on this very night,)

276
00:15:32,907 --> 00:15:34,427
(I met the sun.)

277
00:15:35,427 --> 00:15:36,388
(He is warm)

278
00:15:37,067 --> 00:15:37,868
(and humorous.)

279
00:15:39,468 --> 00:15:40,707
(When he drinks too much,)

280
00:15:41,827 --> 00:15:43,028
(he is even a bit cute.)

281
00:15:46,667 --> 00:15:47,667
Your sun

282
00:15:48,307 --> 00:15:50,028
ended up consuming your life.

283
00:15:51,787 --> 00:15:52,388
Ruoxi,

284
00:15:53,468 --> 00:15:54,268
tell me.

285
00:15:55,228 --> 00:15:56,067
Was it worth it?

286
00:15:57,228 --> 00:15:58,028
Is it worth it?

287
00:16:00,628 --> 00:16:02,108
Maybe it really is.

288
00:16:06,228 --> 00:16:07,187
Ruxue,

289
00:16:07,587 --> 00:16:09,427
(GM's Office)
do you remember who you are?

290
00:16:10,508 --> 00:16:12,667
From your first day here, I told you

291
00:16:13,748 --> 00:16:15,028
everyone here

292
00:16:15,388 --> 00:16:16,228
is a hunter

293
00:16:16,228 --> 00:16:17,628
and also prey.

294
00:16:18,067 --> 00:16:19,148
I'll say it again.

295
00:16:19,827 --> 00:16:20,907
Stay away from troubles.

296
00:16:20,907 --> 00:16:22,067
Focus on your duty.

297
00:16:23,268 --> 00:16:24,707
If you don't want to die,

298
00:16:25,827 --> 00:16:27,108
don't covet

299
00:16:27,108 --> 00:16:28,427
things that aren't yours.

300
00:16:29,628 --> 00:16:30,787
You'll never reach

301
00:16:31,067 --> 00:16:32,587
the sky in this lifetime.

302
00:16:34,907 --> 00:16:36,148
Understood, Ms. Bai.

303
00:16:37,947 --> 00:16:38,667
Off you go.

304
00:16:46,976 --> 00:16:48,228
(GM's Office)

305
00:16:48,228 --> 00:16:49,108
Ruxue.

306
00:17:04,692 --> 00:17:08,366
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

307
00:17:08,665 --> 00:17:11,856
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

308
00:17:13,688 --> 00:17:17,309
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

309
00:17:17,858 --> 00:17:20,657
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

310
00:17:22,128 --> 00:17:25,858
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

311
00:17:26,082 --> 00:17:29,579
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

312
00:17:30,978 --> 00:17:34,665
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

313
00:17:35,303 --> 00:17:40,418
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

314
00:17:41,122 --> 00:17:45,256
♪I feel guilty♪

315
00:17:45,826 --> 00:17:49,570
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

316
00:17:50,434 --> 00:17:53,877
♪Even in tears♪

317
00:17:54,626 --> 00:17:58,540
♪It doesn't matter♪

318
00:17:58,722 --> 00:18:02,545
♪We embrace in dreams♪

319
00:18:03,394 --> 00:18:06,832
♪I let down all my defenses♪

320
00:18:08,066 --> 00:18:11,429
♪Though the story has its end♪

321
00:18:12,194 --> 00:18:20,546
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
